<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-TW">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0, user-scalable=no">
    <title>森之行：新加坡親子冒險</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=M+PLUS+Rounded+1c:wght@400;500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    
    <script>
        tailwind.config = {
            theme: {
                extend: {
                    colors: {
                        'ghibli-bg': '#F2EFE9', // 溫暖米白
                        'ghibli-green': '#6B8E23', // 草綠
                        'ghibli-green-dark': '#556B2F',
                        'ghibli-wood': '#8B5A2B', // 木頭棕
                        'ghibli-blue': '#7EC0EE', // 天空藍
                        'ghibli-yellow': '#F4A460', // 夕陽橘黃
                        'ghibli-text': '#3E4730' // 深苔蘚綠
                    },
                    fontFamily: {
                        sans: ['"M PLUS Rounded 1c"', 'sans-serif'],
                    }
                }
            }
        }
    </script>
    <style>
        body {
            background-color: #F2EFE9;
            color: #3E4730;
            -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;
        }
        /* 隱藏捲軸但保持可捲動 */
        ::-webkit-scrollbar {
            display: none;
        }
        .tab-content {
            display: none;
            animation: fadeIn 0.3s ease-in-out;
        }
        .tab-content.active {
            display: block;
        }
        @keyframes fadeIn {
            from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(10px); }
            to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
        }
        .ghibli-card {
            background-color: #FAFAF7;
            border-radius: 1.5rem;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px -1px rgba(107, 142, 35, 0.1), 0 2px 4px -1px rgba(107, 142, 35, 0.06);
            border: 1px solid rgba(139, 90, 43, 0.1);
        }
        .ghibli-btn {
            background-color: #6B8E23;
            color: white;
            border-radius: 9999px;
            transition: all 0.2s;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 0 #556B2F;
        }
        .ghibli-btn:active {
            transform: translateY(4px);
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 #556B2F;
        }
        .url-btn {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #7EC0EE;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
            border-radius: 9999px;
            margin-top: 0.5rem;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 0.875rem;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="pb-24">

    <header class="bg-ghibli-green text-white p-4 sticky top-0 z-50 shadow-md">
        <h1 class="text-xl font-bold text-center tracking-wider"><i class="fa-solid fa-leaf mr-2"></i>新加坡 5天4夜</h1>
    </header>

    <main class="p-4 max-w-lg mx-auto">

        <section id="tab-plan" class="tab-content active">
            <div class="ghibli-card p-4 mb-6 relative overflow-hidden">
                <div class="absolute -right-4 -top-4 text-ghibli-yellow opacity-20 text-6xl"><i class="fa-solid fa-plane"></i></div>
                <h2 class="font-bold text-lg text-ghibli-wood border-b-2 border-ghibli-wood/20 pb-2 mb-3"><i class="fa-solid fa-ticket mr-2"></i>重要資訊</h2>
                <div class="text-sm space-y-2">
                    <p><span class="font-bold text-ghibli-green-dark">去程：</span> 2026/09/25 14:25 桃園國際機場 <i class="fa-solid fa-plane-departure mx-1"></i></p>
                    <p><span class="font-bold text-ghibli-green-dark">回程：</span> 2026/09/30 11:45 樟宜機場 <i class="fa-solid fa-plane-arrival mx-1"></i></p>
                    <hr class="border-ghibli-wood/10">
                    <p><span class="font-bold text-ghibli-wood">住宿 1：</span> Summer View Hotel</p>
                    <p><span class="font-bold text-ghibli-wood">住宿 2：</span> (代訂處理中)</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="space-y-6">
                <div>
                    <h3 class="bg-ghibli-blue text-white inline-block px-4 py-1 rounded-full font-bold shadow-sm mb-3">Day 1：9/25 文化初探</h3>
                    <div class="border-l-4 border-ghibli-blue/30 ml-4 pl-4 space-y-4">
                        <div class="ghibli-card p-3">
                            <p class="font-bold text-red-500 mb-1"><i class="fa-regular fa-clock"></i> 14:25 航班起飛</p>
                            <p class="text-sm">搭乘星宇航空前往新加坡。</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="ghibli-card p-3">
                            <p class="font-bold text-ghibli-green-dark mb-1">抵達與 Check-in</p>
                            <p class="text-sm">前往 Summer View 飯店放置行李。</p>
                            <a href="https://maps.google.com/?q=Summer+View+Hotel+Singapore" target="_blank" class="text-xs text-blue-500 mt-2 inline-block"><i class="fa-solid fa-location-dot"></i> 開啟地圖</a>
                        </div>
                        <div class="ghibli-card p-3">
                            <p class="font-bold text-ghibli-wood mb-1">小印度區 & 哈芝巷</p>
                            <p class="text-sm">感受印度文化風情與阿拉伯文化色彩。</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="ghibli-card p-3">
                            <p class="font-bold text-ghibli-text mb-1">晚上：克拉碼頭</p>
                            <p class="text-sm">吃晚飯，欣賞河畔夜景。</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div>
                    <h3 class="bg-ghibli-green text-white inline-block px-4 py-1 rounded-full font-bold shadow-sm mb-3">Day 2：9/26 經典獅城</h3>
                    <div class="border-l-4 border-ghibli-green/30 ml-4 pl-4 space-y-4">
                        <div class="ghibli-card p-3">
                            <p class="font-bold text-ghibli-green-dark mb-1">上午：濱海灣花園 & 金沙</p>
                            <p class="text-sm">逛街與午餐。</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="ghibli-card p-3">
                            <p class="font-bold text-ghibli-wood mb-1">下午：牛車水</p>
                            <p class="text-sm">體驗華人文化，購買伴手禮。</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="ghibli-card p-3">
                            <p class="font-bold text-blue-500 mb-1">傍晚：魚尾獅公園</p>
                            <p class="text-sm">必拍經典地標。</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="ghibli-card p-3">
                            <p class="font-bold text-ghibli-text mb-1">晚上：烏節路</p>
                            <p class="text-sm">大型購物中心巡禮，逛街吃飯。</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div>
                    <h3 class="bg-ghibli-yellow text-white inline-block px-4 py-1 rounded-full font-bold shadow-sm mb-3">Day 3：9/27 生態之旅</h3>
                    <div class="border-l-4 border-ghibli-yellow/30 ml-4 pl-4 space-y-4">
                        <div class="ghibli-card p-3 border-2 border-ghibli-yellow">
                            <p class="font-bold text-orange-600 mb-1"><i class="fa-solid fa-star"></i> 全日：動物生態之旅</p>
                            <p class="text-sm mt-1">與動物親密接觸的療癒一天！</p>
                            <ul class="list-disc ml-5 text-sm mt-2 text-gray-600">
                                <li>新加坡動物園 (Singapore Zoo)</li>
                                <li>河川生態園 (River Wonders)</li>
                                <li>鳥園 (Bird Paradise)</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div>
                    <h3 class="bg-purple-400 text-white inline-block px-4 py-1 rounded-full font-bold shadow-sm mb-3">Day 4：9/28 聖淘沙狂歡</h3>
                    <div class="border-l-4 border-purple-300 ml-4 pl-4 space-y-4">
                        <div class="ghibli-card p-3">
                            <p class="font-bold text-purple-600 mb-1">上午：環球影城</p>
                            <p class="text-sm">提早排隊入園！</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="ghibli-card p-3">
                            <p class="font-bold text-red-500 mb-1"><i class="fa-regular fa-clock"></i> 14:00 離開環球影城</p>
                            <p class="text-sm">前往 S.E.A. 海洋館參觀。</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="ghibli-card p-3">
                            <p class="font-bold text-ghibli-wood mb-1">傍晚：斜坡滑車 & 空中吊椅</p>
                            <p class="text-sm">親子刺激活動。</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="ghibli-card p-3">
                            <p class="font-bold text-ghibli-text mb-1">晚上：怡豐城 VivoCity</p>
                            <p class="text-sm">返回本島，大型商場吃晚餐。</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div>
                    <h3 class="bg-blue-400 text-white inline-block px-4 py-1 rounded-full font-bold shadow-sm mb-3">Day 5：9/30 滿載而歸</h3>
                    <div class="border-l-4 border-blue-300 ml-4 pl-4 space-y-4">
                        <div class="ghibli-card p-3">
                            <p class="font-bold text-red-500 mb-1"><i class="fa-regular fa-clock"></i> 10:00 退房</p>
                            <p class="text-sm">準備離開飯店。</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="ghibli-card p-3">
                            <p class="font-bold text-ghibli-green-dark mb-1">前往樟宜機場</p>
                            <p class="text-sm">提早到星耀樟宜看瀑布、逛街玩樂。</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="ghibli-card p-3">
                            <p class="font-bold text-red-500 mb-1"><i class="fa-solid fa-plane-up"></i> 11:45 班機起飛</p>
                            <p class="text-sm">飛回溫暖的台灣，期待下次見！</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section id="tab-guide" class="tab-content">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-ghibli-wood">深度導覽手冊</h2>
            
            <div class="ghibli-card p-4 mb-6">
                <h3 class="font-bold text-lg text-purple-600 mb-2"><i class="fa-solid fa-ticket"></i> 新加坡環球影城 (USS)</h3>
                <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed mb-3">東南亞唯一的一座環球影城。園區雖然不大，但設施非常精華！非常適合帶小朋友來。</p>
                <div class="bg-purple-50 p-3 rounded-lg text-sm mb-3">
                    <strong>💡 攻略筆記：</strong>
                    <ul class="list-disc ml-4 mt-1">
                        <li>開園先衝「變形金剛」或「木乃伊」。</li>
                        <li>有小朋友必去「遠得要命的王國」和「馬達加斯加」。</li>
                        <li>記得自備空水壺，園區內有飲水機可裝水。</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="w-full h-48 bg-gray-200 rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
                    <iframe width="100%" height="100%" frameborder="0" scrolling="no" marginheight="0" marginwidth="0" src="https://www.openstreetmap.org/export/embed.html?bbox=103.8202%2C1.2520%2C103.8250%2C1.2560&amp;layer=mapnik&amp;marker=1.2540%2C103.8226"></iframe>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="ghibli-card p-4 mb-6">
                <h3 class="font-bold text-lg text-ghibli-green-dark mb-2"><i class="fa-solid fa-tree"></i> 濱海灣花園</h3>
                <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed mb-3">彷彿走進阿凡達的世界！這裡有超過上百萬棵植物。超級樹 (Supertree) 晚上還會有燈光秀。</p>
                <div class="bg-green-50 p-3 rounded-lg text-sm">
                    <strong>💡 冷知識：</strong>
                    花穹 (Flower Dome) 是目前世界上最大的玻璃溫室，裡面超級冷，記得幫小朋友帶薄外套！
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="ghibli-card p-4">
                <h3 class="font-bold text-lg text-blue-500 mb-2"><i class="fa-solid fa-water"></i> 星耀樟宜 (Jewel Changi)</h3>
                <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed mb-3">最後一天必逛！室內擁有一座高達40公尺的室內瀑布「雨漩渦」，周圍是熱帶雨林造景。</p>
                <div class="bg-blue-50 p-3 rounded-lg text-sm">
                    <strong>💡 提醒：</strong>
                    建議登機前預留至少 2-3 小時在這裡逛，可以先辦理托運行李後再輕鬆走跳。
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section id="tab-wallet" class="tab-content">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-ghibli-wood">魔法錢包</h2>
            
            <div class="ghibli-card p-4 mb-4 flex justify-between items-center bg-ghibli-yellow/20">
                <label class="font-bold text-sm">目前匯率 (1 SGD = TWD)</label>
                <input type="number" id="exchangeRate" value="23.5" step="0.1" class="w-20 p-1 border rounded text-center font-bold">
            </div>

            <div class="ghibli-card p-4 mb-6">
                <h3 class="font-bold mb-3 border-b pb-2"><i class="fa-solid fa-pen-to-square"></i> 新增花費</h3>
                
                <div class="mb-3">
                    <label class="block text-xs font-bold mb-1 text-gray-500">品項名稱</label>
                    <input type="text" id="expenseName" placeholder="例如：環球影城紀念品" class="w-full p-2 border rounded-lg bg-white">
                </div>

                <div class="mb-3">
                    <label class="block text-xs font-bold mb-1 text-gray-500">輸入算式或金額 (SGD)</label>
                    <div class="flex gap-2">
                        <input type="text" id="expenseCalc" placeholder="例: 50+20*2" class="w-full p-2 border rounded-lg bg-white font-mono">
                        <button onclick="evaluateMath()" class="bg-ghibli-wood text-white px-4 rounded-lg font-bold shadow">=</button>
                    </div>
                    <div class="text-xs text-right text-gray-400 mt-1" id="calcResult">總計: 0 SGD</div>
                </div>

                <div class="flex gap-4 mb-3">
                    <label class="flex items-center gap-1 text-sm">
                        <input type="radio" name="payType" value="cash" checked> 💵 現金
                    </label>
                    <label class="flex items-center gap-1 text-sm">
                        <input type="radio" name="payType" value="card"> 💳 信用卡
                    </label>
                </div>

                <div class="mb-4">
                    <label class="block text-xs font-bold mb-1 text-gray-500">發票/物品照片 (選填)</label>
                    <input type="file" id="expensePhoto" accept="image/*" class="text-xs w-full">
                    <canvas id="photoCanvas" class="hidden"></canvas>
                </div>

                <button onclick="addExpense()" class="ghibli-btn w-full py-3 font-bold text-lg"><i class="fa-solid fa-plus"></i> 記上一筆</button>
            </div>

            <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-3 mb-4">
                <div class="ghibli-card p-3 text-center bg-green-50">
                    <div class="text-xs text-gray-500 font-bold mb-1">💵 現金總計 (SGD)</div>
                    <div class="text-xl font-bold text-green-700" id="totalCash">0</div>
                </div>
                <div class="ghibli-card p-3 text-center bg-blue-50">
                    <div class="text-xs text-gray-500 font-bold mb-1">💳 信用卡總計 (SGD)</div>
                    <div class="text-xl font-bold text-blue-700" id="totalCard">0</div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div id="expenseList" class="space-y-3">
                </div>
            <button onclick="clearExpenses()" class="w-full text-center text-xs text-red-400 mt-6 mt-4 py-2">清除所有記帳紀錄</button>
        </section>

        <section id="tab-lists" class="tab-content">
