            <div class="ghibli-card p-4 mb-6">
                <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-3"><i class="fa-solid fa-suitcase-rolling"></i> 親子必備 CheckList</h3>
                <div id="checklistContainer" class="space-y-2 text-sm">
                    </div>
            </div>

            <div class="ghibli-card p-4">
                <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-3"><i class="fa-solid fa-note-sticky"></i> 個人備忘錄</h3>
                <textarea id="memoInput" rows="4" placeholder="在此輸入隨筆、網址... (輸入網址會自動變成按鈕喔)" class="w-full p-2 border rounded-lg bg-white mb-2 text-sm"></textarea>
                <button onclick="saveMemo()" class="ghibli-btn px-4 py-2 text-sm mb-4">儲存備忘</button>
                
                <div id="memoDisplay" class="bg-white p-3 rounded border text-sm whitespace-pre-wrap min-h-[4rem]"></div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section id="tab-info" class="tab-content">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-ghibli-wood">當地情報局</h2>

            <div class="ghibli-card p-4 mb-4">
                <h3 class="font-bold text-lg text-blue-500 mb-2"><i class="fa-solid fa-cloud-sun-rain"></i> 天氣預報</h3>
                <p class="text-sm mb-2">新加坡屬於熱帶雨林氣候，常常有午後雷陣雨，記得攜帶雨具。</p>
